{"id":101,"date":"2013-05-22T23:17:39","date_gmt":"2013-05-22T23:17:39","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sweetmediasolutions.com\/sfi\/?page_id=101"},"modified":"2026-02-11T12:39:09","modified_gmt":"2026-02-11T20:39:09","slug":"aboutsfi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/aboutsfi\/","title":{"rendered":"About SFI"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2><a style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/about-sfi-foundation\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"margin: 0px 25px 5px 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/About-SFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">About SFI Foundation<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">The SFI Foundation, Inc. (SFI) is a non-profit organization established to issue and administer standards for the quality assurance of specialty performance and racing equipment. The SFI Foundation has served the automotive aftermarket and the motorsports industry since 1978.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/about-sfi-foundation\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/our-history\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"margin: 0px 25px 5px 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Our-History.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">Our History<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">In 1963, a group of racing products manufacturers formed an association known as the Speed Equipment Manufacturers Association, or SEMA. Original organizers deemed the central purpose of the association to be the development of products specifications.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/our-history\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/specs-program\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"margin: 0px 25px 5px 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Specs-Program.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">Specs Program<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">The quality performance specifications program is the heart of the SFI Foundation. The process used to develop each specification is just as important to SFI as the end product itself, the performance specification.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/specs-program\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/test-lab\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"margin: 0px 25px 5px 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Test-Lab.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">Test Lab<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">Opened in 1999, the SFI Test Laboratory was founded to serve the needs of SFI participating manufacturers looking to test their products in an efficient and cost-effective manner.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/test-lab\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/tech-inspector-certification\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft\" style=\"margin: 0px 25px 5px 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Tech-Inspector.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">Tech Inspector Certification<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">The tech inspector certification program was introduced in 1994 and was the first non-product type of program offered by SFI, with the National Hot Rod Association (NHRA) being the first sanctioning body to utilize it.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/tech-inspector-certification\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft  wp-image-5008\" src=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Home-After-Content-Row1-1-1.jpg 1602w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\">Incident Response Training<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">SFI offers an Incident Response Training Program for bringing safety awareness to race track personnel.\u00a0The Drag Race Incident Response Training Program began in 2000 at the request of the NHRA.<br \/>\n<\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/incident-response-training\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><br class=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; display: block; text-align: center;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/section_divider_up.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/h2>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About SFI Foundation The SFI Foundation, Inc. (SFI) is a non-profit organization established to issue and administer standards for the quality assurance of specialty performance and racing equipment. The SFI Foundation has served the automotive aftermarket and the motorsports industry since 1978. Learn More Our History In<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","template":"page-FullWidth.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-101","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/101","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=101"}],"version-history":[{"count":147,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/101\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5011,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/101\/revisions\/5011"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=101"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}